Package fr.warzou.virtualcard.utils.module.file

Class ModuleInnerReader

java.lang.Object
fr.warzou.virtualcard.utils.module.file.ModuleInnerReader
public class ModuleInnerReader
extends Object
Read module raw file.

'//' mean a new indent level.

Example : 

     {
         'a': {
             'b': {
                 'd': 5
             },
             'c': {
                 'e': 6
             }
         }
     }

Path to read 'd' : "a//b//d"

Path to read 'e' : "a//c//e"

Version:
0.0.2
Author:
Warzou
